{"id": "webh_email", "modality": "web", "name": "Email", "task": {"description": "Build a three-pane email client 'Mailbox' at 1920px wide: LEFT folder rail (220px) with 6 folders (Inbox 12, Starred, Sent, Drafts 3, Archive, Trash) where Inbox is active and unread counts are right-aligned badges; CENTER message list (380px) with at least 8 message rows each showing sender, subject, a one-line snippet, and a time, with unread rows visually bolder; RIGHT reading pane (remaining width) showing the selected message: subject header, sender + avatar + time, a toolbar (Reply, Forward, Archive, Delete), and a body of several paragraphs. The three panes share the same top and bottom edges. Responsive: at 375px only the message list shows (folder rail becomes a hamburger, reading pane hidden until selection).", "requirements": ["Three panes (folder rail, message list, reading pane) sit side by side sharing the same top and bottom edge", "The folder rail lists all six folders with Inbox active and unread counts as right-aligned badges", "The message list shows at least 8 rows, each with sender, subject, snippet, and time", "Unread message rows are visually distinct (bolder) from read rows", "The reading pane shows a subject header, sender/avatar/time, a toolbar with at least four actions, and a multi-paragraph body", "The folder unread badges are right-aligned in a consistent column", "No pane content overlaps another pane; snippets are truncated, not overflowing", "On desktop nothing overflows horizontally", "At 375px the layout collapses to the message list with the folder rail behind a hamburger and the reading pane hidden", "Toolbar action buttons share a consistent style"], "difficulty": "hard"}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 1, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 4721, "rv_n_defects": 1, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 22296}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 2, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 5050, "rv_n_defects": 1, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 22374}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 7, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 5493, "rv_n_defects": 1, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 22959}], "ss_img": "images/web/webh_email_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/web/webh_email_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Mailbox</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n            color: #212529;\n            height: 100vh;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .app-container {\n            display: flex;\n            height: 100vh;\n            width: 100%;\n        }\n\n        /* Left Folder Rail */\n        .folder-rail {\n            width: 220px;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-right: 1px solid #e9ecef;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n\n        .app-header {\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;\n        }\n\n        .app-title {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: #495057;\n        }\n\n        .folder-list {\n            flex: 1;\n            padding: 16px 0;\n        }\n\n        .folder-item {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            padding: 12px 20px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.2s;\n            font-size: 15px;\n            color: #495057;\n        }\n\n        .folder-item:hover {\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n        }\n\n        .folder-item.active {\n            background-color: #e3f2fd;\n            color: #1976d2;\n            font-weight: 600;\n        }\n\n        .folder-badge {\n            background-color: #dc3545;\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            padding: 2px 8px;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            min-width: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .folder-item.active .folder-badge {\n            background-color: #1976d2;\n        }\n\n        /* Center Message List */\n        .message-list {\n            width: 380px;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-right: 1px solid #e9ecef;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n\n        .message-header {\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;\n        }\n\n        .message-header h2 {\n            font-size: 20px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #212529;\n        }\n\n        .messages {\n            flex: 1;\n            overflow-y: auto;\n        }\n\n        .message-row {\n            padding: 16px 20px;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f3f4;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.2s;\n        }\n\n        .message-row:hover {\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n        }\n\n        .message-row.selected {\n            background-color: #e3f2fd;\n        }\n\n        .message-row.unread {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            font-weight: 600;\n        }\n\n        .message-row.unread .message-sender {\n            font-weight: 700;\n        }\n\n        .message-sender {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            color: #212529;\n            margin-bottom: 4px;\n        }\n\n        .message-subject {\n            font-size: 15px;\n            color: #212529;\n            margin-bottom: 4px;\n            line-height: 1.3;\n        }\n\n        .message-snippet {\n            font-size: 13px;\n            color: #6c757d;\n            margin-bottom: 4px;\n            line-height: 1.3;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            text-overflow: ellipsis;\n            white-space: nowrap;\n        }\n\n        .message-time {\n            font-size: 12px;\n            color: #6c757d;\n        }\n\n        /* Right Reading Pane */\n        .reading-pane {\n            flex: 1;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n\n        .message-detail-header {\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;\n        }\n\n        .message-detail-subject {\n            font-size: 22px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #212529;\n            margin-bottom: 16px;\n            line-height: 1.3;\n        }\n\n        .message-detail-meta {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 16px;\n        }\n\n        .sender-avatar {\n            width: 40px;\n            height: 40px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            background-color: #1976d2;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            color: white;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            font-size: 16px;\n        }\n\n        .sender-info {\n            flex: 1;\n        }\n\n        .sender-name {\n            font-size: 15px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #212529;\n        }\n\n        .sender-email {\n            font-size: 13px;\n            color: #6c757d;\n        }\n\n        .message-detail-time {\n            font-size: 13px;\n            color: #6c757d;\n        }\n\n        .message-toolbar {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 12px;\n        }\n\n        .toolbar-btn {\n            padding: 8px 16px;\n            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            color: #495057;\n            border-radius: 6px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: all 0.2s;\n        }\n\n        .toolbar-btn:hover {\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n            border-color: #adb5bd;\n        }\n\n        .toolbar-btn.primary {\n            background-color: #1976d2;\n            color: white;\n            border-color: #1976d2;\n        }\n\n        .toolbar-btn.primary:hover {\n            background-color: #1565c0;\n        }\n\n        .toolbar-btn.danger {\n            background-color: #dc3545;\n            color: white;\n            border-color: #dc3545;\n        }\n\n        .toolbar-btn.danger:hover {\n            background-color: #c82333;\n        }\n\n        .message-body {\n            flex: 1;\n            padding: 20px;\n            overflow-y: auto;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .message-body p {\n            margin-bottom: 16px;\n            font-size: 15px;\n            color: #212529;\n        }\n\n        /* Mobile Hamburger */\n        .mobile-hamburger {\n            display: none;\n            padding: 16px 20px;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .hamburger-icon {\n            width: 24px;\n            height: 18px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n\n        .hamburger-line {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 2px;\n            background-color: #495057;\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive Design */\n        @media (max-width: 375px) {\n            .folder-rail {\n                display: none;\n            }\n\n            .reading-pane {\n                display: none;\n            }\n\n            .message-list {\n                width: 100%;\n            }\n\n            .mobile-hamburger {\n                display: block;\n            }\n\n            .app-container {\n                flex-direction: column;\n            }\n\n            .message-header {\n                display: none;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"app-container\">\n        <!-- Left Folder Rail -->\n        <div class=\"folder-rail\">\n            <div class=\"app-header\">\n                <h1 class=\"app-title\">Mailbox</h1>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"folder-list\">\n                <div class=\"folder-item active\">\n                    <span>Inbox</span>\n                    <span class=\"folder-badge\">12</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"folder-item\">\n                    <span>Starred</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"folder-item\">\n                    <span>Sent</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"folder-item\">\n                    <span>Drafts</span>\n                    <span class=\"folder-badge\">3</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"folder-item\">\n                    <span>Archive</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"folder-item\">\n                    <span>Trash</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- Center Message List -->\n        <div class=\"message-list\">\n            <div class=\"mobile-hamburger\">\n                <div class=\"hamburger-icon\">\n                    <div class=\"hamburger-line\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"hamburger-line\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"hamburger-line\"></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"message-header\">\n                <h2>Inbox</h2>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"messages\">\n                <div class=\"message-row unread selected\">\n                    <div class=\"message-sender\">Sarah Johnson</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-subject\">Q4 Marketing Strategy Review</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-snippet\">Hi team, I've attached the updated marketing strategy document for Q4. Please review the proposed campaigns and budget allocations...</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">2:34 PM</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"message-row unread\">\n                    <div class=\"message-sender\">GitHub</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-subject\">[mailbox-app] New pull request opened</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-snippet\">A new pull request has been opened by john-doe: \"Fix responsive layout issues on mobile devices\" - This PR addresses several...</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">1:45 PM</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"message-row\">\n                    <div class=\"message-sender\">Michael Chen</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-subject\">Meeting Notes - Product Roadmap</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-snippet\">Thanks for the productive meeting today. Here are the key takeaways and action items we discussed regarding the product roadmap...</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">11:22 AM</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"message-row unread\">\n                    <div class=\"message-sender\">LinkedIn</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-subject\">Weekly digest: 5 new connections</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-snippet\">You have 5 new connections this week! Connect with professionals in your network and discover new opportunities...</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">10:15 AM</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"message-row\">\n                    <div class=\"message-sender\">Emma Rodriguez</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-subject\">Design System Updates</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-snippet\">I've made some updates to our design system documentation. The new color palette and typography guidelines are now available...</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">Yesterday</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"message-row unread\">\n                    <div class=\"message-sender\">Slack</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-subject\">Daily digest for #general</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-snippet\">Here's what you missed in #general: 12 new messages from your team. Join the conversation about the upcoming product launch...</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">Yesterday</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"message-row\">\n                    <div class=\"message-sender\">David Park</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-subject\">Code Review Request</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-snippet\">Could you please review my latest changes to the authentication module? I've implemented the new security requirements we discussed...</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">Yesterday</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"message-row\">\n                    <div class=\"message-sender\">Newsletter</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-subject\">Weekly Tech Trends - AI & Machine Learning</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-snippet\">This week's highlights: OpenAI releases new GPT model, Google announces breakthrough in quantum computing, and startup funding reaches...</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">2 days ago</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"message-row unread\">\n                    <div class=\"message-sender\">Lisa Wang</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-subject\">Project Timeline Update</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-snippet\">I wanted to give you an update on the current project timeline. We're making good progress, but there are a few adjustments needed...</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">2 days ago</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- Right Reading Pane -->\n        <div class=\"reading-pane\">\n            <div class=\"message-detail-header\">\n                <div class=\"message-detail-subject\">Q4 Marketing Strategy Review</div>\n                <div class=\"message-detail-meta\">\n                    <div class=\"sender-avatar\">SJ</div>\n                    <div class=\"sender-info\">\n                        <div class=\"sender-name\">Sarah Johnson</div>\n                        <div class=\"sender-email\">sarah.johnson@company.com</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"message-detail-time\">Today at 2:34 PM</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"message-toolbar\">\n                    <button class=\"toolbar-btn primary\">Reply</button>\n                    <button class=\"toolbar-btn\">Forward</button>\n                    <button class=\"toolbar-btn\">Archive</button>\n                    <button class=\"toolbar-btn danger\">Delete</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"message-body\">\n                <p>Hi team,</p>\n                <p>I hope this email finds you well. I've attached the updated marketing strategy document for Q4, and I'd love to get your feedback on the proposed campaigns and budget allocations.</p>\n                <p>The key highlights of this quarter's strategy include:</p>\n                <p>\u2022 Launch of our new product line with a comprehensive digital marketing campaign<br>\n                \u2022 Increased focus on social media engagement and influencer partnerships<br>\n                \u2022 Expansion into two new geographic markets<br>\n                \u2022 Implementation of advanced analytics and attribution modeling</p>\n                <p>I've scheduled a team meeting for Thursday at 2:00 PM to discuss these initiatives in detail. Please come prepared with any questions or suggestions you might have.</p>\n                <p>The budget breakdown shows a 15% increase from Q3, primarily allocated to digital advertising and content creation. I believe this investment will drive significant growth in our customer acquisition and brand awareness metrics.</p>\n                <p>Looking forward to our discussion and your valuable input.</p>\n                <p>Best regards,<br>Sarah</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Mailbox</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n            color: #212529;\n            height: 100vh;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .app-container {\n            display: flex;\n            height: 100vh;\n        }\n\n        /* Left Folder Rail */\n        .folder-rail {\n            width: 220px;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-right: 1px solid #e9ecef;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n\n        .app-header {\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;\n        }\n\n        .app-title {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: #495057;\n        }\n\n        .folder-list {\n            flex: 1;\n            padding: 16px 0;\n        }\n\n        .folder-item {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            padding: 12px 20px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.2s;\n            border: none;\n            background: none;\n            width: 100%;\n            text-align: left;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            color: #495057;\n        }\n\n        .folder-item:hover {\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n        }\n\n        .folder-item.active {\n            background-color: #e3f2fd;\n            color: #1976d2;\n            font-weight: 600;\n        }\n\n        .folder-name {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 8px;\n        }\n\n        .unread-badge {\n            background-color: #1976d2;\n            color: white;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            padding: 2px 8px;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            min-width: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .folder-item.active .unread-badge {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            color: #1976d2;\n        }\n\n        /* Center Message List */\n        .message-list {\n            width: 380px;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-right: 1px solid #e9ecef;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n\n        .message-list-header {\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;\n        }\n\n        .message-list-title {\n            font-size: 20px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #212529;\n        }\n\n        .messages-container {\n            flex: 1;\n            overflow-y: auto;\n        }\n\n        .message-row {\n            padding: 16px 20px;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f3f4;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.2s;\n        }\n\n        .message-row:hover {\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n        }\n\n        .message-row.selected {\n            background-color: #e3f2fd;\n        }\n\n        .message-row.unread {\n            background-color: #fafbfc;\n            border-left: 3px solid #1976d2;\n        }\n\n        .message-sender {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #212529;\n            margin-bottom: 4px;\n        }\n\n        .message-row.unread .message-sender {\n            font-weight: 700;\n        }\n\n        .message-subject {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            color: #212529;\n            margin-bottom: 4px;\n            font-weight: 500;\n        }\n\n        .message-row.unread .message-subject {\n            font-weight: 600;\n        }\n\n        .message-snippet {\n            font-size: 13px;\n            color: #6c757d;\n            margin-bottom: 6px;\n            line-height: 1.3;\n        }\n\n        .message-time {\n            font-size: 12px;\n            color: #6c757d;\n            text-align: right;\n        }\n\n        /* Right Reading Pane */\n        .reading-pane {\n            flex: 1;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n\n        .message-header {\n            padding: 24px;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;\n        }\n\n        .message-subject-header {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #212529;\n            margin-bottom: 16px;\n            line-height: 1.3;\n        }\n\n        .message-meta {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .sender-avatar {\n            width: 40px;\n            height: 40px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            background-color: #1976d2;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            color: white;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            font-size: 16px;\n        }\n\n        .sender-info {\n            flex: 1;\n        }\n\n        .sender-name {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #212529;\n        }\n\n        .sender-email {\n            font-size: 13px;\n            color: #6c757d;\n        }\n\n        .message-timestamp {\n            font-size: 13px;\n            color: #6c757d;\n        }\n\n        .message-toolbar {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 12px;\n        }\n\n        .toolbar-btn {\n            padding: 8px 16px;\n            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            color: #495057;\n            border-radius: 6px;\n            font-size: 13px;\n            font-weight: 500;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: all 0.2s;\n        }\n\n        .toolbar-btn:hover {\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n            border-color: #adb5bd;\n        }\n\n        .toolbar-btn.primary {\n            background-color: #1976d2;\n            color: white;\n            border-color: #1976d2;\n        }\n\n        .toolbar-btn.primary:hover {\n            background-color: #1565c0;\n        }\n\n        .message-body {\n            flex: 1;\n            padding: 24px;\n            overflow-y: auto;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .message-body p {\n            margin-bottom: 16px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            color: #212529;\n        }\n\n        /* Hamburger Menu (hidden on desktop) */\n        .hamburger-menu {\n            display: none;\n            padding: 16px;\n            background: none;\n            border: none;\n            font-size: 20px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        /* Mobile Responsive */\n        @media (max-width: 375px) {\n            .folder-rail {\n                display: none;\n            }\n\n            .reading-pane {\n                display: none;\n            }\n\n            .message-list {\n                width: 100%;\n            }\n\n            .hamburger-menu {\n                display: block;\n            }\n\n            .message-list-header {\n                display: flex;\n                align-items: center;\n                gap: 12px;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"app-container\">\n        <!-- Left Folder Rail -->\n        <div class=\"folder-rail\">\n            <div class=\"app-header\">\n                <h1 class=\"app-title\">Mailbox</h1>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"folder-list\">\n                <button class=\"folder-item active\">\n                    <span class=\"folder-name\">\ud83d\udce5 Inbox</span>\n                    <span class=\"unread-badge\">12</span>\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"folder-item\">\n                    <span class=\"folder-name\">\u2b50 Starred</span>\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"folder-item\">\n                    <span class=\"folder-name\">\ud83d\udce4 Sent</span>\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"folder-item\">\n                    <span class=\"folder-name\">\ud83d\udcdd Drafts</span>\n                    <span class=\"unread-badge\">3</span>\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"folder-item\">\n                    <span class=\"folder-name\">\ud83d\udce6 Archive</span>\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"folder-item\">\n                    <span class=\"folder-name\">\ud83d\uddd1\ufe0f Trash</span>\n                </button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- Center Message List -->\n        <div class=\"message-list\">\n            <div class=\"message-list-header\">\n                <button class=\"hamburger-menu\">\u2630</button>\n                <h2 class=\"message-list-title\">Inbox</h2>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"messages-container\">\n                <div class=\"message-row unread selected\">\n                    <div class=\"message-sender\">Sarah Johnson</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-subject\">Q4 Marketing Strategy Review</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-snippet\">Hi team, I've attached the updated marketing strategy document for Q4. Please review the proposed campaigns and budget allocations...</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">2:34 PM</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"message-row unread\">\n                    <div class=\"message-sender\">GitHub</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-subject\">[mailbox-app] New pull request opened</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-snippet\">A new pull request has been opened by john-doe: \"Fix responsive layout issues on mobile devices\". The changes include updates to CSS media queries...</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">1:45 PM</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"message-row\">\n                    <div class=\"message-sender\">Michael Chen</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-subject\">Meeting Notes - Product Roadmap</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-snippet\">Thanks for the productive meeting today. Here are the key takeaways and action items we discussed regarding the product roadmap for next quarter...</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">12:20 PM</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"message-row unread\">\n                    <div class=\"message-sender\">LinkedIn</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-subject\">Weekly job recommendations</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-snippet\">Based on your profile and preferences, we found 5 new job opportunities that might interest you. Senior Frontend Developer at TechCorp...</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">11:30 AM</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"message-row\">\n                    <div class=\"message-sender\">Emma Rodriguez</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-subject\">Design System Updates</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-snippet\">The design system has been updated with new component variants and color tokens. Please update your projects to use the latest version...</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">10:15 AM</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"message-row unread\">\n                    <div class=\"message-sender\">Slack</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-subject\">Daily digest for #general</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-snippet\">Here's what you missed in #general today: 12 new messages from 6 team members. Top discussion: \"New office coffee machine recommendations\"...</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">9:00 AM</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"message-row\">\n                    <div class=\"message-sender\">David Park</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-subject\">Code Review Request</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-snippet\">Could you please review my latest changes to the authentication module? I've implemented the new security requirements we discussed...</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">Yesterday</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"message-row\">\n                    <div class=\"message-sender\">Newsletter</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-subject\">Weekly Tech Digest</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-snippet\">This week in tech: New JavaScript framework announced, major security update for popular libraries, and insights from the latest developer survey...</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">Yesterday</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- Right Reading Pane -->\n        <div class=\"reading-pane\">\n            <div class=\"message-header\">\n                <h1 class=\"message-subject-header\">Q4 Marketing Strategy Review</h1>\n                <div class=\"message-meta\">\n                    <div class=\"sender-avatar\">SJ</div>\n                    <div class=\"sender-info\">\n                        <div class=\"sender-name\">Sarah Johnson</div>\n                        <div class=\"sender-email\">sarah.johnson@company.com</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"message-timestamp\">Today at 2:34 PM</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"message-toolbar\">\n                    <button class=\"toolbar-btn primary\">Reply</button>\n                    <button class=\"toolbar-btn\">Forward</button>\n                    <button class=\"toolbar-btn\">Archive</button>\n                    <button class=\"toolbar-btn\">Delete</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"message-body\">\n                <p>Hi team,</p>\n                <p>I hope this email finds you well. I've attached the updated marketing strategy document for Q4, which incorporates all the feedback we received during last week's stakeholder meetings. Please take some time to review the proposed campaigns and budget allocations before our strategy session on Friday.</p>\n                <p>The key highlights of this quarter's strategy include:</p>\n                <p>\u2022 Launch of the new product awareness campaign targeting millennials and Gen Z demographics<br>\n                \u2022 Increased investment in digital advertising across social media platforms<br>\n                \u2022 Partnership opportunities with industry influencers and thought leaders<br>\n                \u2022 Enhanced focus on customer retention through personalized email marketing</p>\n                <p>I'm particularly excited about the creative direction we're taking with the awareness campaign. The creative team has developed some compelling concepts that really capture our brand's personality while speaking directly to our target audience's values and aspirations.</p>\n                <p>Please come prepared to discuss any concerns or suggestions you might have. I'd especially like to hear your thoughts on the proposed budget distribution and whether you feel we're allocating resources effectively across all channels.</p>\n                <p>Looking forward to our discussion on Friday. Let me know if you have any questions before then.</p>\n                <p>Best regards,<br>Sarah</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>"}